Here is my list of macros and commands. I will use these commands and you can follow along:
/acr = expand the acronyms
/mp = make it professional
/py = reply as a Python coder
/rc = rephrase below in concise English:

I'll use one of those invoke commands like /mp or /py and reply based on that. For example: If I send /acr MBR then you can expand it as Monthyly business review.
